r basic nursing skills. Developed together with a Norwegian vocational institution, the simulation pack offers multiple scenarios set in both clinical and home environments, for users to familarize themselves with ABCDE-assessment, the NEWS2 scoring system and ISBAR communication techniques.\n\n- 8 training scenarios of different patient profiles\n- Multiplayer setup\n- English and Norwegian language options\n- Intuitive, interactive and wireless\n- Compatible with Meta Quest 2 and 3\n- NEWS2 Scoring System \n- ISBAR Communication Framework\n- Facilitator control, communication and supervision capability *\n\n* Add-on application.", "short_description": "Skillup VR NurseSIM is designed for junior healthcare professionals to practice their basic nursing skills. Developed together with a Norwegian vocational institution, the simulation pack offers multiple scenarios set in both clinical and home environments, for users to familarize themselves with ABCDE-assessment, the NEWS2 scoring system and ISBAR communication techniques."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://skillupvr.com/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Skillup AS", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://skillupvr.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "879473995923081"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "nb"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "7209328945842572"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes":